Package dev.lyze.gdxtinyvg.commands.paths

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    UnitPathArcCircleCommand
    Draws an circle segment between the current and the target point.
    UnitPathArcEllipseCommand
    Draws an ellipse segment between the current and the target point.
    UnitPathCloseCommand
    A straight line is drawn to the start location of the current segment.
    UnitPathCommand  
    UnitPathCubicBezierCommand
    The cubic bezier instruction draws a Bézier curve with two control points.
    UnitPathHorizontalLineCommand
    The horizontal line instruction draws a straight horizontal line to a given x coordinate.
    UnitPathLineCommand
    The line instruction draws a straight line to the position.
    UnitPathQuadraticBezierCommand
    The quadratic bezier instruction draws a Bézier curve with a single control point.
    UnitPathSegment  
    UnitPathVerticalLineCommand
    The vertical line instruction draws a straight horizontal line to a given x coordinate.
